Committee: Education
1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to education; to amend sections 79-215 and
2 79-2,136, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to change provisions
3 relating to the admission of students and require each school board
4 to allow certain students that are not residents of the school
5 district to participate in extracurricular activities as prescribed;
6 to harmonize provisions; and to repeal the original sections.
7 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
